Package: countdown
Title: A Countdown Timer for HTML Presentations, Documents, and Web Apps
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Garrick", "Aden-Buie", , "garrick@adenbuie.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7111-0077"))
Description: Countdown to something amazing. 'countdown' makes it easy to
    drop a simple countdown timer into slides and HTML documents written
    in 'R Markdown'. Integrates fully into 'Shiny' apps.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://pkg.garrickadenbuie.com/countdown/,
